{
  "stem": "22447.2",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One was senior Jewish chaplain, Isaac Levy, one was the RAF chaplain, squadron leader Sanker, and Captain Hartman, he was second army chaplain.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then we had a little service, and they take-- take everybody's name, just in case you get mentioned in the paper somewhere.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There must have been about 25-- 20, 25.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One of the fellows has an all argument with Isaac Levy, because he married took place in the Bayswater shul, and the marriage didn't work out, so that was his fault.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said, all right.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After that, about two weeks later, I got a letter from home.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Who is this Captain Hartman?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He's going to send a letter to my sister at the time, that he saw me, I'm all right.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And got well and everything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'll come home all right.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I always kept that letter.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's on exhibition at the Sternberg Center in London.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She said, they caught such a fright.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because if you get a letter from an officer, there's only one thought that comes to your mind.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they had such a fright when the saw the-- from the Jewish chaplain, it could only mean one thing.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Till they opened it and they read it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he was the only one in the six years of war, that ever took the trouble to send home a letter and say that they'd seen me.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'd seen other parties-- Did you know any of the other 25 people who were there?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they were from all parts of--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Or from the RAF, [INAUDIBLE] all different branches of the services.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nobody wanted to mix with the military police, anyway, so it didn't make any difference.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't see any.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't come across any, .",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
